c: 2
v: 150
t: "Wherever you are Ë¹O ProphetËº, turn your face towards the Sacred Mosque. And wherever you Ë¹believersËº are, face towards it, so that people will have no argument against you, except the wrongdoers among them. Do not fear them; fear Me, so that I may Ë¹continue toËº perfect My favour upon you and so you may be Ë¹rightlyËº guided"